<p><a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0312649940/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=0312649940&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=gaye-20" target="_blank">Artisan Pizza and Flatbread in Five Minutes a Day</a><img title="Grinding Wheat with the Incredible WonderMill   Plus a Giveaway   Backdoor Survival" alt="Grinding Wheat with the Incredible WonderMill   Plus a Giveaway   Backdoor Survival" src="http://www.assoc-amazon.com/e/ir?t=gaye-20&amp;l=as2&amp;o=1&amp;a=0312649940" width="1" height="1" border="0" />:  What can I say?  You will do fine with the recipe I have shared today, but the book is well worth it and I believe in supporting these two fabulous authors that really do care about your success.  There is also <a title="Healthy Bread in Five" href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0312545525/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=continmoti-20&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=0312545525" target="_blank">Healthy Bread in Five Minutes a Day: 100 New Recipes Featuring Whole Grains, Fruits, Vegetables, and Gluten-Free Ingredients</a><img style="margin: 0px;" alt="Grinding Wheat with the Incredible WonderMill   Plus a Giveaway   Backdoor Survival" src="http://www.assoc-amazon.com/e/ir?t=continmoti-20&amp;l=as2&amp;o=1&amp;a=0312545525" width="1" height="1" border="0" title="Grinding Wheat with the Incredible WonderMill   Plus a Giveaway   Backdoor Survival" /> from the same authors.</p>
