<p>I will be first to admit that there are a lot of lists floating around with suggested uses for coffee filters but most include all kinds of uses that are nice, but totally irrelevant to the prepper.  After all, if you are in experiencing hard times, or a survival situation, do you really care about preventing your fine china from chipping?</p>
