t love this stuff.</p>
<p>A year ago I posted an article on the many uses of duct tape for survival.  It went viral.  Even so, I think that as a team, we can do better.  I would like to see 50, 80 or even 101 uses of duct tape for survival purposes.<a href="http://www.backdoorsurvival.com/duct-tape-for-survival/" target="_blank"></a></p>
