estival</strong></span></span></a><span style="color: #c0504d;"><span style="color: #9e1f63;">.</span></span>  Alex Smith, the author of <a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/1482353903/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&#38;camp=1789&#38;creative=390957&#38;creativeASIN=1482353903&#38;linkCode=as2&#38;tag=continmoti-20" target="_blank">Getting Home</a> shares his answers to my questions and is also providing one of my readers with a free copy of his book.</p>
