<h3>THE FINAL WORD</h3>
<p><span style="color: #000000;">Getting Home is not a long book. Instead, it is concise and gets right the to point in a clear, easy to read and logical manner.  It has an especially good section on day packs (purse, backpack, laptop bag) and it even inspired me to keep one with me for those times that I need more than an EDC (every day carry) but less than a bug out bag.  It is an especially good value at $3.99 for the Kindle version.</span></p>
